-- Ford says evaluating bids for Jaguar, Land Rover
-- 
-- Thu Jul 19, 2007 11:28am EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2007/07/19/us-ford-jaguar-landrover-idUSN1940755220070719

 

 DETROIT  (Reuters) - Ford Motor Co.( F.N ) said on Thursday it has had contact with interested parties for its Land Rover and Jaguar luxury brands and is evaluating the level of interest. 

 "We have had contact with interested parties," said John Gardiner, a spokesman for Ford's European luxury brand, referring to Jaguar and Land Rover. "We are actively evaluating the level of interest." (Reporting by  Poornima Gupta )